      "description": "Presenting a peerless example of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom-state condition, having been meticulously maintained to the highest standards of preservation. Every detail, from the pristine interior upholstery to the lustrous, original exterior finish, reflects a commitment to perfection. Mechanically indistinguishable from new, this unit offers an uncompromising driving experience for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than the extraordinary.",
