    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to be selling my absolute pride and joy, but it\u2019s time for a new chapter. This car has been my total baby\u2014always kept in a climate-controlled garage, hand-washed every weekend, and it still smells brand new inside! It\u2019s in truly stunning condition and drives like it just left the showroom floor. If you're looking for a ride that's been treated with nothing but love and perfection, you\u2019ve found it. I'd love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have!",
      "price": 46500.0,
