    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a breathtaking time capsule, meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment and presented in true showroom condition. The original factory paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free of swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of untouched luxury; the premium leather remains supple and matte, the dashboard is devoid of any sun exposure, and every switchgear click feels as crisp as the day it was manufactured. Mechanically, this car is peerless, benefiting from a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule with every service documented. From the flawless undercarriage to the pristine engine bay, no detail has been overlooked. This is not just a used car; it is a museum-quality example that drives with the same tightness and precision it possessed on the showroom floor. For the discerning buyer who demands perfection, this is the definitive choice.",
      "price": 44500.0,
