      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an investment-grade vehicle maintained to the most exacting standards of automotive preservation. This specimen exhibits a flawless exterior profile and an interior that remains in showroom state, devoid of any discernible wear. Mechanically peerless and aesthetically uncompromising, this vehicle represents a benchmark of quality for the discerning enthusiast. We invite a private viewing to confirm its exceptional status.",
