    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is a total gem\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, keeping it garaged and spotless inside and out. It drives like a dream and is seriously in pristine condition. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I\u2019m ready for it to find a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
