    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-quality 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Titanium Silver over Black Nappa leather. At its heart is the S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system for optimized valve timing across the rev range. This unit has undergone a comprehensive preventative maintenance suite, including documented rod bearing replacement and proactive subframe reinforcement to ensure maximum torsional rigidity. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox offers short, tactile throws, feeding power through a variable M-differential lock. The suspension geometry is dialed to factory specifications, utilizing fresh bushings and Sachs dampers for that quintessential 'as-new' damping profile. Zero pixel degradation in the instrument cluster and no bolster wear on the seating surfaces. This is a turn-key mechanical masterpiece for the serious collector.",
